/* NaCl brine.  The liquid-activity slot is the electrolyte model -- selected
   like any activity model (one word: pitzer).  The salt's ions + solubility live
   in NaCl.dat (called by name); nothing chemical is re-typed here.  Self-contained:
   components copied into constant/components/. */
components       ( water NaCl );
activityModel    { model eNRTL; }
equationOfState  { model idealGas; }
